data.description:
Finally, a lightweight COLOR version of Pebble's original Big Time watchface! Pebble's easiest-to-read digital face, with selectable color and these new configurable features:
1. Ability to set each digit to a different color (red/green for Christmas, blue/white for Hanukkah, purple/gold/white/orange for Festivus);
2. An optional analog second hand (we know how useful they can be);
3. An optional date and two-week calendar, which appears upon wrist shake (duration is configurable);
4. An optional battery indicator; and
5. An optional Bluetooth-connection icon to alert you if your watch has disconnected from your phone (yes, it'll vibrate on disconnect/reconnect).

Also, for a short time only and for no adequately-explored reason other than it's winter here in the Northern Hemisphere, optional snow-covered digits (no impact on battery life)!
